 Package : clamav
 Date    : November 20, 2014
 Affected: Business Server 1.0
 _______________________________________________________________________

 Problem Description:

 ClamAV 0.98.5 addresses several reported potential security bugs.
 
 Certain javascript files causes ClamAV to segfault when scanned with
 the -a (list archived files) (CVE-2013-6497).
 _______________________________________________________________________

 References:

 http://cve.mitre.org/cgi-bin/cvename.cgi?name=CVE-2013-6497
 https://bugzilla.clamav.net/show_bug.cgi?id=11088
 http://blog.clamav.net/2014/11/clamav-0985-has-been-released.html
